parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioner fan can cause reduced airflow, inadequate cooling, and increased temperatures inside the vehicle, which can lead to discomfort, fatigue, and potentially even heat-related illnesses.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rear Cargo Door Lock Failure with Remote Keyless Entry
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear cargo door lock to respond to the remote keyless entry system can compromise the security of the vehicle and its contents, making it easier for thieves to access the cargo area.
symptoms: The rear cargo door lock does not respond to the remote keyless entry system
the rear cargo door lock does not unlock or lock when using the remote keyless entry
the rear cargo door lock is stuck in the locked or unlocked position.
